OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FIn the US, attempts by senators to
OL,7,Flimit the power exercised by US
OL,8,FPresident Donald Trump also failed as
OL,9,Fthe Senate rejected a war powers
OL,10,Fmeasure demanding congressional
OL,11,Fapproval before further attacks.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, in the UK, Prime Minister
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer was forced to defend
OL,15,Fhis stance on the war, after President
OL,16,FTrump hit out at him as "not Winston
OL,17,FChurchill".
OL,19,FUS submarine sinks Iranian warship
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/24
