OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FOn the fifth day of fighting, a US
OL,7,Fsubmarine sunk the Iranian vessel IRIS
OL,8,FDena with a torpedo in international
OL,9,Fwaters.
OL,11,FUS Defence Secretary Pete Hegseth
OL,12,Fconfirmed that an American submarine
OL,13,Fhad torpedoed an Iranian warship that
OL,14,F"thought it was safe in international
OL,15,Fwaters".
OL,17,FSri Lanka's Foreign Minister Vijitha
OL,18,FHerath told parliament that its navy
OL,19,Freceived information that the IRIS
OL,20,FDena, with 180 people on board, was in
OL,21,Fdistress and sinking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
