OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FNavy spokesman Commander Buddhika
OL,7,FSampath said by the time rescue ships
OL,8,Freached the location, there was no
OL,9,Fsign of the ship in distress and
OL,10,F"there were only some oil patches and
OL,11,Flife rafts. We found people floating
OL,12,Fon the water."
OL,14,FHe said the 32 people were rescued and
OL,15,Fadmitted to a hospital in Galle, a
OL,16,Ftown on Sri Lanka's southern coast.
OL,17,FThe bodies recovered were also being
OL,18,Fbrought to land, he said.
