OL,11,FNato member
OL,13,FAs the conflict spiralled, Turkey said
OL,14,FNato defences intercepted a ballistic
OL,15,Fmissile launched from Iran on
OL,16,FWednesday before it entered Turkey's
OL,17,Fairspace.
