OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio told
OL,7,FTurkish Foreign Minister Hakan Fidan
OL,8,Fthat attacks on Turkey's territory are
OL,9,Funacceptable and pledged full US
OL,10,Fsupport after an Iranian missile
OL,11,Fheaded toward the country was shot
OL,12,Fdown, the State Department said on
OL,13,FWednesday.
OL,15,FStrikes on Iran
OL,17,FLate Wednesday, Israeli forces said
OL,18,Fthey were beginning a broad "wave of
OL,19,Fstrikes" on Tehran and other major
OL,20,Fcities, targeting Iranian leadership
OL,21,Fand security forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/24
