OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FAirstrikes have also been reported in
OL,7,Fthe Iranian cities of Urmiah, Isfahan
OL,8,Fand Kermanshah. Overnight, the IDF had
OL,9,Ftargeted what it described as command
OL,10,Fcentres used by Iran's feared internal
OL,11,Fsecurity forces and the Basij militia.
OL,13,FThere appears to be little appetite
OL,14,Ffor de-escalation despite the killing
OL,15,Fof Iran's Supreme Leader, Ali Khamenei
OL,16,Fin the initial attack on Saturday.
OL,17,FHegseth confirmed that US operations
OL,18,Fin Iran were in their "very early"
OL,19,Fdays.
