OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,F"Four days in, we have only just begun
OL,7,Fto fight," he said.
OL,9,FMore than 1,000 people have been
OL,10,Fkilled in Iran since the war began,
OL,11,Faccording to the US-based Human Rights
OL,12,FActivists News Agency.
OL,14,FEarlier, the IDF claimed an Israeli F-
OL,15,F35 fighter jet shot down a manned
OL,16,FIranian warplane in Tehran on
OL,17,FWednesday, in what it described as the
OL,18,F"first shootdown in history of a
OL,19,Fmanned fighter aircraft by an F-35
OL,20,F'Adir' fighter jet.
