OL,6,FThe level of bombardment in Iran was
OL,7,Fsevere enough
OL,9,FIran draws closer to selecting a new
OL,10,Fleader
OL,12,FIran's leaders are scrambling to
OL,13,Freplace Khamenei, who ruled the
OL,14,Fcountry for 37 years. It's only the
OL,15,Fsecond time since the 1979 Islamic
OL,16,FRevolution that a new supreme leader
OL,17,Fis being chosen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/24
