OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FPotential candidates range from hard-
OL,7,Fliners committed to confrontation with
OL,8,Fthe West to reformists who seek
OL,9,Fdiplomatic engagement. Mojtaba
OL,10,FKhamenei, Khamenei's son, has long
OL,11,Fbeen considered among them ` though he
OL,12,Fhas never been elected or appointed to
OL,13,Fa government position.
OL,15,FIn a sign that Iran's leadership will
OL,16,Fonly seek to consolidate its power as
OL,17,Fit faces its biggest crisis in
OL,18,Fdecades, the head of the judiciary
OL,19,Fwarned that "those who cooperate with
OL,20,Fthe enemy in any way will be
OL,21,Fconsidered an enemy."
