OL,6,FThe Israeli defence minister
OL,7,Fthreatened whoever Iran picks to be
OL,8,Fthe country's next supreme leader.
OL,10,F"Every leader appointed by the Iranian
OL,11,Fterror regime to continue and lead the
OL,12,Fplan to destroy Israel, to threaten
OL,13,Fthe United States and the free world
OL,14,Fand the countries of the region, and
OL,15,Fto suppress the Iranian people ` will
OL,16,Fbe a target for elimination," Katz
OL,17,Fwrote on X.
