OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FIran continued retaliatory firing
OL,7,Fmissiles and drone strikes against its
OL,8,FGulf neighbours and Israel. Iran's
OL,9,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard said
OL,10,Fit targeted Irbil in Iraq, two
OL,11,Fmilitary bases in Kuwait, and two US
OL,12,Fwarships.
OL,14,FThe guard said via Iranian state
OL,15,Ftelevision that it is prepared for the
OL,16,F"complete destruction of the region's
OL,17,Fmilitary and economic infrastructure."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/24
