OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,F"The continued mischief and deception
OL,7,Fby the United States in the region
OL,8,Fwill come at the cost of the complete
OL,9,Fdestruction of the region's military
OL,10,Fand economic infrastructure," it said.
OL,12,FIt alleges, without offering evidence,
OL,13,Fthat the US military was using
OL,14,F"civilian facilities ... as cover."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/24
