OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FIn Iran, state television has said the
OL,7,Fmourning ceremony for the late Supreme
OL,8,FLeader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei has been
OL,9,Fpostponed, and will be held later
OL,10,Fafter intense strikes targeted Tehran.
OL,11,FA top cleric said it was "close" to
OL,12,Fchoosing the next leader.
OL,14,FThe ceremony was set to take place on
OL,15,FWednesday evening at the Grand Mosalla
OL,16,Fof Tehran.
OL,18,FCommunication with the country has
OL,19,Fbeen difficult, with internet
OL,20,Fmonitoring group NetBlocks saying Iran
OL,21,Fhas been offline now for 100 hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/24
