OL,6,FThe nationwide shutdown, imposed when
OL,7,Fthe war began Saturday, is being
OL,8,Floosened as the Israeli military says
OL,9,Fincoming missile fire has dropped in
OL,10,Frecent days.
OL,12,FHowever, Israelis are still "spending
OL,13,Fa lot of time in shelters,"
OL,14,Facknowledged Brig. Gen. Effie Defrin,
OL,15,Fa military spokesperson.
