OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FAt a Pentagon briefing Wednesday, the
OL,7,FUS Joint Chiefs of Staff chairman,
OL,8,FGen. Dan Caine, said that the number
OL,9,Fof ballistic missiles fired off by
OL,10,FIran is down by 86% from the first day
OL,11,Fof the war, and that there's been a
OL,12,F23% drop in the last 24 hours.
OL,14,FNews of easing the restrictions comes
OL,15,Feven as Israel ups its military
OL,16,Fengagements, advancing into Lebanon in
OL,17,Fa push to eliminate Iran-backed
OL,18,Fmilitia, Hezbollah.
OL,20,FRising oil prices
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/24
