OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FIran has carried out attacks on
OL,7,Fpassing ships and vowed to continue to
OL,8,Fdo so, forcing many shipping companies
OL,9,Fto suspend operations in the area.
OL,11,FUS president Donald Trump floated the
OL,12,Fidea of escorting oil tankers through
OL,13,Fthe Strait of Hormuz with the US Navy.
OL,15,FFour US Service Members killed during
OL,16,Fthe conflict with Iran named
OL,18,FFour US service members killed in a
OL,19,Fdeadly Iranian drone strike in Kuwait
OL,20,Fhave been named.
