OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FThey were named as: Captain Cody A.
OL,7,FKhork, 35, of Winter Haven, Florida;
OL,8,FSergeant Noah L Tietjens, 42, of
OL,9,FBellevue, Nebraska; Sergeant Nicole M.
OL,10,FAmor, 39, of White Bear Lake,
OL,11,FMinnesota, and Specialist Declan J.
OL,12,FCoady, 20, of West Des Moines, Iowa.
OL,14,FThe Pentagon said they were all killed
OL,15,Fby a drone that struck where they were
OL,16,Fworking in Port Shuabia, Kuwait, on
OL,17,FSunday.
OL,19,FTwo other soldiers who were killed in
OL,20,Fthe strike have not been publicly
OL,21,Fidentified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/24
