OL,11,FBritish nationals abroad
OL,13,FBritish nationals are being advised to
OL,14,Ffollow the instructions of local
OL,15,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,16,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,17,Fofficials expect to change rapidly.
