OL,3,CIsrael begins 'new wave' of strikes on
OL,4,CTehran, as US sinks Iranian warship
OL,6,FSpeaking at Prime Minister's Questions
OL,7,Fon Wednesday, Starmer said that more
OL,8,Fthan 1,000 British Nationals arrived
OL,9,Fback in the UK from the UAE on
OL,10,Fcommercial flights on Tuesday.
OL,12,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,13,Ftwo further government-chartered
OL,14,Fflights will take off from Oman "in
OL,15,Fthe coming days".
OL,17,FBritish Airways announced it will
OL,18,Foperate two more flights between the
OL,19,Fcapital Muscat and London Heathrow, on
OL,20,FFriday and Saturday.
